    description:
      "Lajitas Casa Grande: Spacious Four Bedroom Vacation Rental Home in an Upscale Resort CommunityThe SpaceLajitas Casa Grande is conveniently located in the resort community of Lajitas but is not affiliated with the resort. Guests normally have access to the golf course, restaurants, and more. Easy access to Big Bend National Park, Big Bend Ranch State Park, and Terlingua Ghost Town.\n\nLajitas Texas has long been known as \"the ultimate hideout\". This remote resort community offers first class comforts among the rugged mountains of Big Bend. Lajitas Casa Grande continues that tradition with a spacious four-bedroom home for your family or group.\n \nLajitas Casa Grande is ideally located for easy access to resort facilities in Lajitas (except the private pool) and adventures throughout the Big Bend. Please note that at particularly busy times, the resort may limit access to the golf course, dining options, or other resort amenities. We recommend that guests check with Lajitas Resort to verify access to any resort amenities they may plan to utilize. Enjoy world-class golfing at Black Jack's Crossing. Pamper yourself at the Agave Spa. Saddle up at the Equestrian Center. Visit the famous Terlingua Ghost town. Ride the rapids along the Rio Grande. Or venture into Big Bend National Park or Big Bend Ranch State Park.\n \nWhen you’re not busy enjoying the amenities of the resort or the adventures of the mountains and desert, you and your family or group will have plenty of space to relax and unwind at Casa Grande. The large living room, open dining room, and well stocked kitchen provide ample indoor space for hanging out in air-conditioned comfort. The front porch and rear decks are great for relaxing outside while enjoying mountain scenery, breathtaking sunrises and sunsets, or mesmerizing starry nights. The four bedrooms are comfortably furnished with high quality beds and linens for a great night’s sleep. Two full bathrooms add to the convenience.  Various books and games are provided for everyone’s enjoyment.\n \nWe all need an occasional break from our everyday life. Lajitas Casa Grande will provide you with a once in a lifetime escape and adventure. Of course, it does not have to be JUST once in a lifetime. You are welcome to come back again and again. We hope and suspect that you will.\n\nBlack Jack's Crossing Golf Course\nTexas Outside ranked Black Jack’s Crossing the “Number One Resort Course in Texas”. Golfweek magazine named Black Jack’s the “Best New Course in Texas.” It has also been named the number-four “Best Place To Play in Texas” by the Dallas Morning News and the number-seven “Best Course To Play in Texas” by Golfweek.\n\nThe Agave Spa\nThe Agave Spa is a beautiful oasis in the desert. They offer a variety of spa treatments that are designed to nurture and relax. Specialty massages, facials and body treatments are also available. Choose from a variety of treatments to help relax and rejuvenate your mind, body and spirit.\n\nLajitas Equestrian Center\nThe Lajitas Equestrian Center offers a variety of services; including trail rides, riding lessons, basic and advanced riding clinics and boarding. They strive to match horse and rider to make your experience an enjoyable one, whatever your skill level.\n\nShooting Activities\nPut your shooting skills to the test at the five stand sporting clay shoot, cowboy action shoot, combat course, rifle or pistol range.",
